h to resurgence, and that graded resurgence underlies a\npotentially rigorous definition of general QFTs. The mass gap and the Theta\nangle dependence of vacuum energy are calculated from first principles, and are\nin accord with large-N and lattice results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2012 21:09:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-06"}
