 range of M_H is already either ruled\nout or on the edge of detection. Finally we investigated the possibility that\nthe heavy Higgs is close in mass to the light Higgs, providing additional h/H\n--> bb rate, as well as confounding the extraction of properties of the Higgs\nbosons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2012 01:15:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2012 17:17:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-05"}
